<L>__{exterior central park reservoir day (later)}
<A>__{runners of both sexes and all ages are huffing and puffing as they jog along the track that circles the reservoir. one of the runners looks behind him at the sound of approaching footfalls and screams.}
<B>__{ghostly jogger}
<A>__{a ghost jogger is loping along at a pretty fair pace. other runners stumble and run screaming into the park as he passes them. seemingly oblivious to the effect he's having, the ghost jogger puts two fingers to his skeletal neck and checks his watch as if taking his pulse.}
